Remember,

56
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:37,580
even though the /ɪ/ is more relaxed

57
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:39,900
and the shorter part of the diphthong,

58
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:42,760
you need to pronounce it completely.

59
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:49,360
Now, let's practice the /aɪ/ sound in some words.

60
